00:11:01.670 --> 00:11:05.198
We have our common sense
and our common experience.

00:11:06.057 --> 00:11:10.148
So I ask, if you are
a health care executive:

00:11:10.172 --> 00:11:12.876
Do you know how many
of your patients run out of food

00:11:12.900 --> 00:11:15.806
or struggle to pay the rent
at the end of the month?

00:11:15.830 --> 00:11:18.206
Is that data on your scorecard,

00:11:18.230 --> 00:11:21.019
shaping your business and your bonuses?

00:11:21.796 --> 00:11:23.716
If you are a politician:

00:11:23.740 --> 00:11:28.019
